    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Something into which to look that may have consequences for this issue is whether or not Bazel allows the output files generated by a rule to exist or not-exist according to the content of the input files. If not, and I suspect not, fulfilling this issue would erect an obstacle to [building gRPC Python with Bazel](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/issues/8079), which although a long-term goal is something we very much want."
